{"tid":1885100,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你老母，變撚態！青龍頭掟寵物落街15死10傷 冷血狂徒落網","createTime":"2020-02-18T05:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T03:10:55.000Z","uid":257961,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"87a78b5be9f55889b0eb6af3be77d8665b45ba07","tid":1885100,"uid":257961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:13:31.000Z","msg":"2月14日情人節當日下午，深井青龍頭豪景花園有25隻寵物遭冷血狂徒由高處掟落山坡，屍橫遍野，翌日保安員（15日）再發現3隻受傷貓，事件令人齒冷，警方經調查後，昨晚（17日）於荃灣區拘捕49歲姓葉男子，他涉嫌「殘酷對待動物」。葉現正被扣留調查。據悉，葉在荃灣警署內被捕<br />\n<br />\n案發當日下午1時許，25隻寵物被發現倒卧在豪景花園第19座附近山坡，部份更倒卧在樓下的溝渠和附近的水池上，當中有15隻動物已被愛護動物協會職員確認死亡，另外10隻則仍有生命迹象，被送往搶救。當時愛協回應傳媒查詢時表示，當中仍生存的包括5隻貓和5隻龍貓，另外有9隻龍貓、1隻天竺鼠、1隻寵物鼠、1隻寵物雀、1隻貓及2隻兔已經死去，即傷亡寵物數字總數應為25隻。愛協相信牠們是被人從高處擲下，涉及虐待動物行為。"},{"pid":"efe1ac654d54b0824cc5c2a7dc881edea2dec21b","tid":1885100,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />rip"},{"pid":"14a34aae7c016c7910368ef94df61ec351c5aa84","tid":1885100,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12a0c23206d846a5d3be652d5911880125d5943","tid":1885100,"uid":18999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"正一仆街"},{"pid":"23854effd01b05df535359487019b5930c7448df","tid":1885100,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"會判坐幾耐